==Description==
Mr. Paul is a sailor grobo living in the [[Citadel Island harbour|harbour]] of [[Citadel Island]]. He is responsible for the ferry and its passengers.

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
When [[Twinsen]] needed to go from Citadel to [[Desert Island]], Paul steered it. He also checked if Twinsen had a [[Ferry ticket|ticket]] or not.

